Html5 portion of the crossplatform application. All changes should be carried out in this project.

The project contains an ant build task which builds the project and copies it to the appropriate project. 
Currently only the android and ios projects have been implemented.

It is assumed that you have previously checked out the android project to the same directory as the html5 project.
basedir/html5
basedir/android
basedir/ios

Also the sencha command tool is required it can be found here, http://www.sencha.com/products/sencha-cmd/download

run > sencha ant build-android

this builds and copies the files to the android project.

or 

run > sencha ant build-ios

this builds and copies the files to the ios project.
